s/1489097242321428482/sQSUN_M6_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Libs of TikTok", "username": "libsoftiktok"}, "content": "Ilhan Omar secured MILLIONS of tax dollars for a Minneapolis health clinic that was run by\u2026 her sister!\n\nI\u2019m sure there\u2019s nothing to see here!", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 67262}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2050454874022728106", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZf89zE2", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 56, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "retard", "id": 8594942, "raw_content": "", "author": "journalist", "created": 1777724848469, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "charwoman", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZf89zE2.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/houseofyogi/status/2050454874022728106?s=61", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "How Elizabeth Warren killed Spirit Airlines \u2014 In case you\u2019ve forgotten.", "last_comment_created": 1777730891971, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 15, "score_up": 56, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 1524, "created": 1777701512000, "id": "2050454874022728106", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2022863065864376321/beWsnmEd_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Yogi", "username": "Houseofyogi"}, "content": "Spirit Airlines died tonight at the hands of the socialist crusader, Elizabeth Warren\n\nShe must be so proud to add another casket to her achievements.\n\nTonight at 3am, Spirit turns off the lights. 14,000 jobs gone. 30+ smaller airports lose service.\n\nJetBlue offered $3.8 BILLION", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 35198}}, "post_flair_text": "RETARD", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZf9GjO0", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 30, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8595334, "raw_content": "\u201cWhen the CDC was thinking about mandating the chickenpox vaccine for your children, they did a study.\n\nThe person they hired to do that study was a scientist named Gary Goldman, who did a long-term study in California.\n\nWhat he found is that if you give the chickenpox vaccine, mass vaccinate, it stops chickenpox, but causes shingle epidemics later on; which is 20x deadlier.\n\nDespite those studies, we mandated for American children in this country, but in Europe they don\u2019t.\n\nIf you go to the British National Health Service website right now, you can read that it will say, \u201cWe do not recommend chickenpox vaccines  because it causes shingles epidemics later on\u2026 and that\u2019s the problem.\n(Check the link here: nhs.uk/vaccinations/c\u2026)\n\nYou can\u2019t say this product is going to prevent this particular disease, but you have to look at the long-term implications.\u201d\n\nhttps://x.com/thehealthb0t/status/2050530803004960968?s=46", "author": "TheLawofOne-", "created": 1777737433125, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Littleirishmaid", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Chickenpox vaccines caused the shingles epidemic. ", "last_comment_created": 1777740229537, "content": "<p>\u201cWhen the CDC was thinking about mandating the chickenpox vaccine for your children, they did a study.</p>\n<p>The person they hired to do that study was a scientist named Gary Goldman, who did a long-term study in California.</p>\n<p>What he found is that if you give the chickenpox vaccine, mass vaccinate, it stops chickenpox, but causes shingle epidemics later on; which is 20x deadlier.</p>\n<p>Despite those studies, we mandated for American children in this country, but in Europe they don\u2019t.</p>\n<p>If you go to the British National Health Service website right now, you can read that it will say, \u201cWe do not recommend chickenpox vaccines  because it causes shingles epidemics later on\u2026 and that\u2019s the problem.\n(Check the link here: nhs.uk/vaccinations/c\u2026)</p>\n<p>You can\u2019t say this product is going to prevent this particular disease, but you have to look at the long-term implications.\u201d</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/thehealthb0t/status/2050530803004960968?s=46\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/thehealthb0t/status/2050530803004960968?s=46</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZf88byt", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 290, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8594443, "raw_content": "", "author": "I-am-Orlando", "created": 1777692287074, "profile_picture": "TEnkk5XkT6JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "HaSumBro", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "m